1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with detecting visual corruptions in videos using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses ideas and methods from Multiple Instance Learning (MIL) setting. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for automated testing of graphics units. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with testing graphics units. 
5. cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a real-time system for automated testing of graphics units.
